01:22:07,840 --> 01:22:10,753
was the fact that not only
did the cast come back

1032
01:22:10,843 --> 01:22:14,211
but all of the main
collaborators, those living,

1033
01:22:14,346 --> 01:22:18,590
and we had as our director
