01:22:24,398 --> 01:22:30,269
with a new designer of the
costumes, was Milena Canonero,

1037
01:22:30,362 --> 01:22:32,273
picking up from the wonderful work

1038
01:22:32,364 --> 01:22:34,981
that Johnny Johnstone
had done on the first film

1039
01:22:35,075 --> 01:22:39,285
and Theodora Van Runkle
had done on the second film.

