01:22:46,170 --> 01:22:47,962
And associate editor was Lisa Fruchtman,

1043
01:22:48,046 --> 01:22:50,458
who had worked also on <i>Apocalypse Now.</i>

1044
01:22:50,549 --> 01:22:52,756
So it was a family,

1045
01:22:53,385 --> 01:22:57,754
both in the crew and the team.

